      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Step into luxury with this absolutely pristine vehicle! It is in mint condition, looking and driving just like it did the day it left the showroom. Meticulously cared for with a flawless finish and a spotless interior, this car is a rare find for anyone seeking perfection on the road.",
      "price": 48500.0,
