    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good, reliable condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owner. The exterior paint retains a nice shine, though upon close inspection, you will find some minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scratch on the passenger side door. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free; while the leather shows some light creasing on the driver's side bolster, there are no rips or stains. All electronic features and climate controls are fully functional. Mechanically, the car performs well with a consistent maintenance record, though the tires will likely need replacement within the next 10,000 miles. It is a solid, dependable choice for anyone looking for a quality pre-owned vehicle that has many miles left to give.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic work. The exterior has several deep scratches, visible rust on the wheel arches, and a dent in the rear bumper. The interior shows heavy wear, including tears in the fabric seats and a cracked dashboard. Mechanically, the car is struggling; the engine has a noticeable knock, and the transmission slips when shifting. It is being sold strictly as-is and would be best suited as a project car or for parts. A full inspection and major repairs are necessary before it can be considered roadworthy.",
      "price": 4500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
