      "description": "We are pleased to present an automotive specimen of unparalleled distinction. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, exhibiting an uncompromising level of care and preservation that satisfies the most discerning collector. Every surface reflects factory-original integrity, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, smoke-free cabin. Mechanical performance is seamless, mirroring its aesthetic perfection. This is an investment-grade acquisition for those who demand nothing less than the absolute standard of excellence.",
